+
+`Grep "HasFullPageRoute" src/Hexalith.FrontComposer.Contracts` returned **ZERO matches**. Story 2-2's `IFrontComposerRegistry` does NOT yet expose `bool HasFullPageRoute(string commandTypeName)`.
