+    /// <returns>A read-only list of cuwarning: in the working copy of 'src/Hexalith.FrontComposer.Contracts/Shortcuts/ShortcutBinding.cs', LF will be replaced by CRLF the next time Git touches it
rrently registered shortcuts.</returns>
